(17208, 'Delmonkast 10mg 14 f.c. tabs.', 'ديلمونكاست 10 مجم 14 قرص', '48', '64', 'Montelukast', 'Delta pharma', 'Tab', 'أقراص', '', 'Asthma.anti-inflammatory.leukotriene antagonist', '10mg', 'Montelukast is indicated for:
